text: Ocotea jorge-escobarii is a species of plant in the family Lauraceae. The tree is endemic to Honduras and Nicaragua in Central America.Nelson, C. 1998. IUCN Red List.org Ocotea jorge-escobarii . downloaded on 22 August 2007.
